title: 154: The Trader Joe's Fall Haul Episode (Sept. '21 Edition)
itunes:title: The Trader Joe's Fall Haul Episode (Sept. '21 Edition)
description: In this episode, Lisa and the gang are taste-tasting a whopping 14 items from Trader Joe’s! Stuff like their vegan enchilada casserole, 2 kinds of pumpkin yogurt, 2 vegan dips that are out of this world, a tasty tortilla chip, oatmeal bites, and SO MUCH MORE! Plus, a breaking chews food find that becomes part of the haul!!! There’s only one thing left to do… PUSH PLAY NOW! And make sure you listen all the way through to find out how to win this week’s prize!
itunes:summary: It’s that time again… TJ’s has new items, and we’re trying them this week on Chew The Right Thing!
itunes:author: Lisa Lillien
dc:creator: Lisa Lillien
